{{Description|Sailfish are known for their incredible speed, long bill, and their striking sail-like dorsal fin. It's sleek body is built for fast swimming, allowing it to dart through water in bursts of speed. They are found in tropical and warmer ocean waters.|Bestiary Entry}}

